arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActorPlayer, sWorldName)

	Hydra.QActorWait(ID_PRIEST_ENTRANCE, 2)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_PRIEST_ENTRANCE, LOC_PRIEST_DOOR, "NPC_WALK_FAST", true)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONVO_PRIEST_03x, ID_PRIEST_ENTRANCE)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(ID_PRIEST_ENTRANCE, LOC_PRIEST_END, "NPC_WALK_FAST", true)
	Hydra.QActorFaceSameAsActor(ID_PRIEST_ENTRANCE, LOC_PRIEST_END) 
	Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(ID_PRIEST_ENTRANCE, CONVO_PRIEST_03x)
	Hydra.QActorWait(ID_PRIEST_ENTRANCE, 0.5)

	Hydra.QActorEventSendToActor(ID_PRIEST_ENTRANCE, "PRIEST_MOVE", idSelf)
	
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

	Hydra.ActorEnable(ID_AXE)
	Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(ID_PRIEST_ENTRANCE, ANIM_CHANT)
	Hydra.QActorWait(ID_PRIEST_ENTRANCE, 3)
	Hydra.WaitForQEmpty(ID_PRIEST_ENTRANCE)

	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(LOC_BLAST_GHOST_01, FX_BURST)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(LOC_BLAST_GHOST_02, FX_BURST)
		
	Hydra.QActorEventSendToActor(ID_PRIEST_ENTRANCE, "PLACE_WEAPON", idSelf)
	
end

function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)
		
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(LOC_BLAST_PRE_1, FX_BURST)
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(LOC_BLAST_PRE_2, FX_BURST)
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(LOC_BLAST_PRE_3, FX_BURST)
	Hydra.ActorsEnableLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "DEMON")
	Hydra.Wait(1)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(CONVO_PRIEST_06, ID_PRIEST_ENTRANCE)
	
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(LOC_BLAST_AXE, FX_BURST)
	Hydra.ActorDisable(ID_AXE)
	Hydra.ActorSetAnimSetOverride(ID_PRIEST_ENTRANCE, ANIM_WOUNDED)
	
	Hydra.QActorEventSendToActor(ID_PRIEST_ENTRANCE, "AXE_DESTROYED", idSelf)
		
	--[[
	if (strLevelArea == S_ZONE_NAME_FRAC) then
		Hydra.WeatherOverride(strWorld, "weather_dungeon_generic");
	end	
	]]--
	
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	Hydra.ItemGiveQuestItemToPlayer(idActorPlayer, ITEM_AXE, "DSQ_QST_Frac_Inheritance_02")
	Hydra.ActorDisable(ID_AXE_DESK)
end
